titles.title: To suspend temporarily the duty on 1-Propanone, 2-methyl-1-[4- (methylthio)phenyl]-2-(4- morpholinyl)-(9cl).
To suspend temporarily the duty on 1-Propanone, 2-methyl-1-[4- (methylthio)phenyl]-2-(4- morpholinyl)-(9cl).

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Ways and Means.
Referred to the Subcommittee on Trade.

bill.summary: Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend, through December 31, 2008, the duty on 1-Propanone, 2-methyl-1-[4- (methylthio)phenyl]-2-(4- morpholinyl)-(9cl).
